name: In Memoriam
description: This is a piece in homage to my first DSLR camera which died on the 16th of June 2021 the evening after I finished making my piece for the second week of the NFThunderdome competition. It is a photo mosaic of almost all of the photographs I have taken with this camera since I recieved it from my Mum in 2016 whilst I was in India. This camera has meant a lot to me, and is where I developed and found my love for photography and the documentation of the world we live in. | ~19000 images 11547x866px | Canon 400D, Lightroom, and AdreaMosaic | Photographed from 27/05/2106 - 16/06/2021 |
